Peanut Butter Cottage Cheese Cookie Dough                gf
  --Jake Cohen
  
1 lb low-fat cottage cheese
1/2 c creamy peanut butter or any nut/seed butter
1/4 c maple syrup
2 tsp vanilla 
3 c almond flour
1 c dark chocolate chips

In a blender, combine the cottage cheese, peanut butter, maple syrup, and vanilla, then pur√©e until very smooth. Transfer to a bowl and stir in the almond flour until well incorporated, then fold in the chocolate chips. Store in an airtight container in the refrigerator.
These are not for baking!
